answers.text: There is not enough information to answer the question.
If a number is divisible by 5, it is also divisible by 10.
If a number is divisible by 1, it is also divisible by 2.
If the last 3 digits of a number are divisible by 2, then the number is divisible by 4.
If a number is divisible by 2 and 3, it is also divisible by 6.
